Modification and packaging notice (2026-07-15):

The previous title-only draft was replaced with a private topic-selection
workflow. The new implementation adds a fixed account profile, structured
upstream-material intake, a 72-hour attention-signal policy, dual-evidence and
truth gates, hidden candidate scoring, five-platform adaptation, and the
ContentTopicPlan output contract. It does not include network scrapers and does
not track publishing history or performance data. The runtime package includes
one deterministic provider-contract validator for orchestrated request/result,
path, hash, and artifact validation. Repository synchronization does not install
the Skill into a user-level Skill directory.
